    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering 315 hp through a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The engine benefits from a verified IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced water pump, ensuring thermal efficiency and structural integrity. Performance is anchored by its rear-engine layout, providing exceptional mechanical grip under acceleration, complemented by a multi-link rear suspension and upgraded Bilstein dampers for precise lateral load management. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over vented rotors, offering consistent bite and minimal fade. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the chassis remains rigid and the throttle response is sharp, making it a definitive analog driving machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
